<P>
"Peaceable Kingdom" is the best new show on TV this fall. The stories are 
heartwarming, fresh, entertaining and devoid of the violence that continually 
bombards the tube. The show also displays a positive image of our Los Angeles 
Zoo to the rest of the country. 
</P>
<P>
Susan Hancock, North Hollywood 
</P>
</TEXT>
