</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102289-0095 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 124113 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 22, 1989, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 2; Advance Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Stained glass window emerged unscathed as Watsonville's 100-year-old St. 
Patrick's Catholic Church was badly damaged. The church is expected to be 
razed. JIM MENDENHALL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
