Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Life's a breeze -- Everyday worries appear to be miles away from this 
sailboat near Redondo Beach. ALAN HAGMAN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102289-0122 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 124182 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
