<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Winning Colors struggled to a fourth-place finish in the $156,500 Aqueduct 
Budweiser Breeders' Cup Handicap for fillies and mares 3 and up, as Wakonda, 
