<DOCID> 124414 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 22, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 19; Column 4; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
219 words 
</P>
