<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102289-0225 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 124441 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 22, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
