DISASTER VICTIMS; DISASTER RELIEF; ORANGE COUNTY FIRE DEPARTMENT; FIREFIGHTING 
EQUIPMENT; FIREFIGHTERS; OAKLAND (CA); NIMITZ FREEWAY; HELM, BUCK ALVIN 
